The paper deals with interpreting neural net responses, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also proposes a new method for interpretability, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper evaluates the usefulness of the proposed method in explaining model behavior, which could also fall under natural language processing (cs.CL) if the model being evaluated is a language model.
